{"tid":950618,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【支爆】支那九鼎擬出售富通保險或賺16億美元　傳與周大福最快下周達成協議","createTime":"2018-12-21T16:27:58.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-22T00:23:03.000Z","uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"c34ff08d3824295cd5cdb84f03712ddada214cfe","tid":950618,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-21T16:27:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20181221/large/1545376804_3daf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20181221%2Flarge%2F1545376804_3daf.jpg&h=72058d91&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/realtime/article/20181221/59055316\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181221%2F59055316&d=pWRanps2weUGMQ9AXhniRKMP9SZiTpIcsXSGftWU1%2BE%3D&h=4ef3afa3\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181221%2F59055316&h=492bc39f\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/realtime/article/20181221/59055316</a><br />\n<br />\n彭博引述知情人士透露，周大福正在就收購富通保險進行獨家談判。消息稱，富通保險的所有者支那九鼎投資和鄭氏家族旗下的周大福期望最早在下周達成協議。協議對富通保險的估值可能接近30億美元（約234.6億港元）。<br />\n<br />\n知情人士指，目前尚未做出最終決定，談判仍有可能失敗，從而讓九鼎投資可以與其他競購者恢復商談。<br />\n<br />\n據彭博新聞社報道，這家香港保險公司吸引了永明金融和亞洲另類資產管理公司PAG等潛在買家的興趣，PAG已與新加坡的GIC Pte就可能聯合競標進行了談判。<br />\n<br />\n周大福及九鼎投資，均不評論事件。<br />\n<br />\n九鼎投資2015年同意以13.8億美元（逾107億港元）收購Ageas SA旗下香港壽險業務，其後更名為富通保險。<br />\n<br />\n彭博匯總的數據顯示，亞太公司今年涉足的保險行業併購交易已達到510億美元，比2017年同期成長23%。"},{"pid":"342d7b0be44d4fe1d7c0f5b1042fc8ba7469ee72","tid":950618,"uid":14918,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-21T16:51:08.000Z","msg":"香港地產霸權真係好勁<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fb1b425f8242cb46fcd1080047edce463d8c01ba","tid":950618,"uid":35815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-22T00:23:03.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}